{
  "texts": [
    "However, this gain in pixel-wise accuracy comes at the cost of a significant drop in topological continuity.",
    "This trade-off motivates our final architecture, which integrates these components within a single stage to achieve a more optimal balance.",
    "Qualitative AnalysisTo visually substantiate our quantitative results, we present a qualitative analysis in Figure 4 and Figure 5.",
    "These figures illustrate our model's superior ability to preserve road network integrity in challenging real-world scenarios.",
    "Figure 4 showcases several examples where our hybrid model excels compared to strong baselines like SegFormer and VMamba."
  ]
